      <div class="tag">Original Research</div>
      <h1>Illinois Tool Works (ITW)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">A transparent, two-stage discounted cash flow valuation of Illinois Tool Works — using FY2025 actuals, disclosed assumptions, and one final number.</p>
      <p class="date">Compiled by Gemini 3.1 · Data: FY2025</p>
    </div>
  </div>

